            We keep a live ledger of the entire portfolio: every position, every move, overall performance
            and individual entries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="benefit card">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M12 1a11 11 0 1 0 11 11A11.013 11.013 0 0 0 12 1m1 6v5l4 2l-1 1l-5-3V7z"
            ></path></svg
          >
